// Arkage wordmark. Letterforms inherit `currentColor` (set the color on the
// parent: black on the light nav, ivory on the dark footer); the triangle stays
// orange as the brand accent. Width is derived from the height prop so the SVG
// keeps its aspect ratio without needing any inline style expression.
